                        "<p>Have each person quickly introduces themself with their first name (“I’m Amanda or Miss Amanda, and I teach about bugs”)</p>",
                        "<p>We will tell also introduce the camera equipment.</p>",
                        "<p>The first task asks students to draw moths. If they ask, “What is a moth?” we can tell them a moth is a type of insect. They should draw what they think a moth might be. </p>",
